  ----- MISCELLANEOUS FORMATTING COMMANDS -----


   ,PP      start paragraph
   ,PPNL N  paragraph needs N lines on same page
   ,PPSP N  paragraph space N lines
   ,PPSI N  paragraph single indent


   ,BFS  N  boldface - strike N times at printout


   ,PC   C  character for delimiting print strings
   ,MMC  C  mail merge character
   ,PADC C  pad character for non-paddable spaces
            on printout


   ,*       comment line
